name: A Second Look at Virtual Living
description: This image, "A Second Look at Virtual Living" was created with the assistance of artificial intelligence (AI). The process for creating this image included using a text prompt, algorithms, and artificial intelligence. The Snowpixel App was used in this process of creating this unique image. The image will be interpreted differently through the eyes and imagination of the viewer. The concept behind this image was Metaverse travel appears different from one 3D virtual world to another. Often it takes a second look to see what each 3D virtual world has to offer.
